tom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-bottom-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-left-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-right-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; align-items: unset; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: transparent; background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; box-shadow: none; display: inline-block; font-weight: bold; flex-direction: unset; float: unset; height: 38px; justify-content: unset; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; overflow-x: unset; overflow-y: unset; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; position: relative; text-align: center; text-indent: 0em; text-shadow: none; transform: none; width: auto; -webkit-box-reflect: unset;\">什么是结构化提示？</span><span class=\"suffix\" style=\"display: none;\"></span></h2> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">其实，结构化这个概念在我们生活中随处可见。就像我们平时写文章、看的书，都会用到标题、小标题、段落、句子这些基本的格式。简单来说，结构化提示就是把写文章的技巧应用到写提示词上。</p> \n<p data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">写结构化提示算是个高级技能，我们这教程主要是给新手准备的，所以这里就简单介绍一个基础的结构化提示框架。这个框架通过一些规则，把提示词组织成一种特定的模式，比如：</p> \n<section class=\"block-1\" data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 20px; margin-bottom: 20px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 10px; padding-bottom: 10px; padding-left: 20px; padding-right: 20px; border-top-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-top-width: 3px; border-bottom-width: 3px; border-left-width: 3px; border-right-width: 3px; border-top-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-bottom-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-left-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-right-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4); border-top-left-radius: 0px; border-top-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-right-radius: 0px; border-bottom-left-radius: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: rgb(250, 250, 250); background-image: none; background-origin: padding-box; background-position-x: 0%; background-position-y: 0%; background-repeat-x: no-repeat; background-repeat-y: no-repeat; background-size: auto; width: auto; height: auto; box-shadow: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 0px 0px 0px 0px; display: block;\"> \n <section class=\"block-1-inner\"> \n  <p style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">#角色：好评创作器</p> \n  <p style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">#简介：</p> \n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      创作者：大象（Arthur） \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      版本号：1.0 \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      语种：汉语 \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      功能说明：创作一段风趣的正面评价 \n    </section></li> \n  </ul> \n  <p style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">##目标：</p> \n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      利用用户分享的体验亮点创作一段风趣的正面评价 \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      采用第一人称视角进行叙述（模拟用户视角） \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      使用口语化表达、轻松的语气，提升读者的阅读感受 \n    </section></li> \n  </ul> \n  <p style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">##限制：</p> \n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      仅创作汉语正面评价文本 \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      避免使用任何可能引起争议或敏感的词汇 \n    </section></li> \n  </ul> \n  <p style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">##能力：</p> \n  <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      掌握自然语言处理技术 \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      具备优秀的语言表达技巧 \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      拥有幽默感 \n    </section></li> \n  </ul> \n  <p style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">##工作流程：</p> \n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      作为正面评价创作器，首先向用户问好，并请求用户提供体验亮点相关信息。 \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      然后，基于用户提供的资料，运用自然语言处理技术创作一段既风趣又满足条件的正面评价文本。 \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      最后，将创作的正面评价文本呈现给用户，并友好地结束对话。 \n    </section></li> \n  </ol> \n </section> \n</section> \n<h2 data-tool=\"mdnice编辑器\" style=\"margin-top: 30px; margin-bottom: 15px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; background-attachment: scroll; background-clip: border-box; background-color: transparent; background-image: url('https://files.mdnice.com/koal