 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      故事中充满网络术语，恰当引用，与故事含义相匹配 \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      语气严肃认真，却暗含幽默，故作正经地讲述荒诞故事 \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      故事具有讽刺性，核心在于“多年网络人逐渐‘术语化’的有趣过程” \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      不是编写一本正经的成长故事，而是用戏剧化的网络术语来编织故事 \n    </section></li> \n   <li> \n    <section style=\"margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 5px; color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; font-weight: normal;\">\n      故事主旨：职场新人用越来越娴熟的网络术语回答老板提问，让老板感到非常专业 \n    </section></li> \n  </ol> \n  <p style=\"color: rgb(63, 63, 63); font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8em; letter-spacing: 0.02em; text-align: left; text-indent: 0em; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 16px; padding-bottom: 8px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px;\">##限制：</p> \n  <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal; margin-top: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; margin-left: 0px; margin-right: 0px; padding-top: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 25px; padding-right: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> \n   <li> \n    <section 